Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.00,0:01:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创界山是分了七层\N由神仙居住的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.10,0:01:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了打倒支配这座山的\N邪恶帝皇多恶达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.67,0:01:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们边与多恶达的魔神战斗\N一边向第七界层进发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.64,0:01:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了冰雪世界\N第四界层的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.41,0:01:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来到了胡娜拉像\N身处的野野神殿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.08,0:01:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但被埋伏在这里的残三兄弟\N的魔神合体达的攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.55,0:02:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我们不能接近胡娜拉像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.36,0:02:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸用尽了最后的力量\N使出火炎登龙剑打倒了合体达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.80,0:02:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却连他的生命也燃烧尽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.10,0:02:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令第四界层\N回复了原来的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.20,0:02:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了找到\N令龙神丸重生的复活圣水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.57,0:02:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上到第五界层了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.04,0:02:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也会是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.38,0:02:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十一话\N魔界王子，虎王登场！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.59,0:02:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样啊？东哥罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.06,0:02:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了打倒了龙神丸的我们\N的厉害了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.70,0:02:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样第五界层便安全了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.07,0:02:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前失去了的界层便再一次\N用我们的力量去支配它吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.40,0:02:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发白日梦应适可而止了\N残兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.20,0:02:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.18,0:02:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是打倒了龙神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.81,0:03:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你们的合体达也重伤\N在修理中呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.15,0:03:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你们不知道吗？\N渡他们现正去第五界层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.10,0:03:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.42,0:03:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我东哥罗是不会说谎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.89,0:03:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，第五界层是我们的部下\N邪恶污烟掌管的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.80,0:03:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们命令他去收拾渡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.83,0:03:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？用口说很简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.17,0:03:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.11,0:03:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说战部渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.41,0:03:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是你们想的\N那么天真的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.58,0:03:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收声！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.91,0:03:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我们一日还在\N也没有你出场的份儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.25,0:03:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，你便做那小鬼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.12,0:03:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，虎王大人的保父便可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.75,0:03:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，对，保父\N男人当妈妈，大蠢材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.32,0:03:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和虎王大人越来越亲近呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.60,0:03:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.50,0:03:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是虎王大人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.00,0:04:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是虎王大人吗？\N虎王大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.30,0:04:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎王大人\N铁皮兵也是我们的家巨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.42,0:04:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以乱来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.75,0:04:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是太闷\N所以想运动一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.49,0:04:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是东哥罗\N我要到下界玩啊，去准备吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.67,0:04:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N下界不是虎王大人可以去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.64,0:04:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父王多恶达大人\N吩咐过我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.20,0:04:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我很无聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.51,0:04:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎王大人，不可以任性啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.90,0:04:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，要我留在这里的话\N你便做“那个”给我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.29,0:04:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“那个”的意思\N是那件事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.86,0:04:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，快点干吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.72,0:04:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了你就乖乖回房去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.05,0:04:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.40,0:04:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了，那么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.97,0:05:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样便可以了吗？虎王大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.30,0:05:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.80,0:05:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪虎丸\N和我一起去胡闹一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧！邪虎丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.43,0:05:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧！老虎变身！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.35,0:05:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，就这样去下界吧\N去吧！邪虎丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.06,0:06:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛\N第五界层是个怎样的地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.80,0:06:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道呢，可以肯定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.24,0:06:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有不知道第五界层某处的\N西里露森林内有复活圣水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.30,0:06:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论怎样也要取到那圣水\N令龙神丸复活过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.05,0:06:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸，你等我\N我一定会令你恢复原状的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.62,0:06:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该很快会看见第五界层了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.80,0:06:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？古拿玛\N这是什么第五界层？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.57,0:06:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.57,0:06:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真危险呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.31,0:06:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.58,0:06:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛，加油！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.45,0:06:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是为了炽热的友情\N我要加油！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.50,0:07:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了，这里便是第五界层呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.47,0:07:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.54,0:07:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.35,0:07:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.05,0:07:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一次\N到空气这么差的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.85,0:07:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么了？伤风了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.62,0:07:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么？火美子\N你吸了这样的空气也没事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.63,0:07:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从后面放出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.50,0:07:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再污染空气了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.76,0:08:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.03,0:08:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是好孩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.66,0:08:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很努力工作，这是奖励
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.87,0:09:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍法，退烟之术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.45,0:09:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是真奇怪呢\N一个人也看不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.62,0:09:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里满布黑烟的城\N哪里会有森林啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.86,0:09:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么声音？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.44,0:09:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你精神吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因为担心你，所以又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.14,0:09:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然以前这条村\N有很多你的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.88,0:09:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在好像只剩下你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.05,0:09:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天…\N如果那家伙没有来的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.80,0:09:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏吧！\N这么丑的自然没有需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.90,0:10:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,树木、花朵、鸟儿和虫\N也不需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.87,0:10:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由今天开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.01,0:10:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这转变为充满美的污烟\N和清香废气的了不起的都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.11,0:10:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐！停手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.90,0:10:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们的关系\N这条向日葵村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.32,0:10:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成了动物和昆虫\N也不能住的村了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.99,0:10:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你这么坚强地成长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.96,0:10:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！少年…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.96,0:10:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有点事想请教一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.73,0:10:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是什么人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.07,0:10:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！那是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.30,0:10:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是希度罗拿的同伴吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.00,0:10:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希度罗拿？那是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.97,0:10:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别扮傻了\N来到这条村的人全部也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.08,0:10:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一见面便怀疑人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.31,0:10:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年\N我虽不清楚发生了什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.75,0:10:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你打开心窗讲来听听吧\N也许我们可以帮你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.85,0:10:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收声，说得这么漂亮\N便以为我会信你们吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.56,0:10:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！等等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.63,0:11:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！请等等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.03,0:11:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，这样的话在下也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.27,0:11:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.50,0:11:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅\N真拿他没办法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.58,0:11:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些水是什么回事？\N令我非常恶心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.85,0:11:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅，没事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.08,0:11:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，渡，想想办法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.10,0:11:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛，让他想想办法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.65,0:11:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是了\N真是要人费心的老师呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.60,0:11:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔的情况有点怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.30,0:11:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了？这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.96,0:11:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅！\N到底什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.67,0:11:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救我啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.61,0:11:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡，你看那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.08,0:11:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为希度罗拿的关系\N令村内的生物巨大化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.25,0:11:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小渡，快点想想办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.86,0:12:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子，龙神丸拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.63,0:12:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.40,0:12:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.17,0:12:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.58,0:12:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很…很硬！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.59,0:12:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜拳！猜拳！\N包、剪、槌！胜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.40,0:12:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子还要再猜拳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.85,0:12:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么不经大脑的话？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.07,0:12:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的头差点被剪下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.30,0:12:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个，你快点用你的\N奇怪飞镖令它们睡觉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.21,0:12:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.60,0:13:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已…已不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.66,0:13:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡！这样的话在下便…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.16,0:13:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…这个…在下是开玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.33,0:13:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡，振作点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.84,0:13:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛，火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.50,0:13:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好！火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.45,0:13:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难缠的家伙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.52,0:13:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗？渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.32,0:13:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们，古拿玛，火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.19,0:13:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算什么\N真是悠闲的大叔呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.86,0:13:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只蟹一次吃不完啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.60,0:14:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N战部渡来了第五界层？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.39,0:14:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚残酷将军联络我的\N我也吓了一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.43,0:14:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗？\N一发现便立刻消灭他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.97,0:14:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请交给我吧，污烟大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.34,0:14:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，如果你把渡收拾了\N下个月加你两倍人工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.84,0:14:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？\N但是…万一失败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.98,0:14:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便这辈子也别想拿人工了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.85,0:14:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.15,0:14:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.45,0:14:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手！放手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.25,0:14:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？发生了什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.29,0:14:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是蝴蝶蛹\N你是说那个小鬼拿着的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.00,0:15:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.84,0:15:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对自然有敏感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.97,0:15:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶、花朵和树木\N全部都很讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.95,0:15:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.50,0:15:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.68,0:15:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西这么重要吗？\N小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.62,0:15:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你也一起去地府吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是制造什么的工场？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.83,0:15:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论是什么\N令天空染成黑色也不能原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.10,0:15:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是最在意刚才的少年\N到底去了哪里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.74,0:15:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的悲叫声是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.24,0:15:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.58,0:15:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米罗！米罗！米罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.40,0:15:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈！\N米罗！米罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.25,0:15:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼，你觉悟吧\N这便是违抗我的惩罚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.92,0:16:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵在这溶液里是很舒服的\N只一会儿便变白骨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.96,0:16:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希度罗拿大人\N请你饶恕米罗吧，我求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.50,0:16:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收声！干吧，铁皮兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.97,0:16:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.54,0:16:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.38,0:16:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是刚才的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.21,0:16:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是忙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.92,0:16:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那家伙打下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.42,0:16:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧！奇怪珠！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.40,0:16:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.96,0:16:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我便是又有趣又有型\N世人的英雄，救世主--渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.83,0:16:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.03,0:16:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？你便是渡吗？\N竟阻着我行刑？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.60,0:16:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直升战机部队，出动！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.48,0:16:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是多恶达魔神的直升战机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.35,0:16:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说\N这里是多恶达的工场吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.15,0:16:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，我们村内的人\N被迫制造那些魔神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.99,0:17:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,这样便一定要救村内的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.16,0:17:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下去叫战神丸出来\N古拿玛，你也叫空神丸来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.16,0:17:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.07,0:17:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪珠 red！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.80,0:17:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.51,0:17:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.45,0:17:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火…火美子\N没有收拾他们的忍法吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.48,0:17:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一招很厉害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.35,0:17:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你帮我拿着这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.69,0:17:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.02,0:17:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍法变身之术！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.40,0:17:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材！\N现在变成狸猫有什么用？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.51,0:17:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  失败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.01,0:17:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直升战机部队\N把那些小鬼们收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.34,0:18:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.22,0:18:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了在下便糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.39,0:18:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野牛武一郎流交叉字斩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.19,0:18:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.63,0:18:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.40,0:18:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗？老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.57,0:18:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，古拿玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.20,0:18:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师，你骑上空神丸吧\N一起收拾他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.10,0:18:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，各位快逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.03,0:18:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.16,0:18:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的战部渡，你看着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.76,0:18:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈！ 米罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.20,0:18:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.03,0:18:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，赶快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.84,0:19:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样便让我亲手消灭你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.18,0:19:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！\N渡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.81,0:19:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正蠢材！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.82,0:19:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅，古拿玛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.86,0:19:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶\N这时如果龙神丸在的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.29,0:19:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.73,0:19:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之要引他离开大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.33,0:19:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，今次到我当你的对手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.37,0:19:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正蠢材，竟自己来送死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.61,0:19:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.85,0:19:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，小鬼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.12,0:19:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.35,0:19:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼\N不要以为可以一直逃下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.50,0:19:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去会被干掉的\N不快点想办法的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.03,0:20:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.14,0:20:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来追我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.52,0:20:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？我真聪明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有点不妙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.23,0:20:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快逃啊！这处要爆炸了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.86,0:20:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆…爆炸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.33,0:20:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动！快动啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.67,0:20:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在这里便糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.84,0:20:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我记着啊，臭小子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.54,0:20:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了！成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.18,0:20:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多谢你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.42,0:20:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N刚才我说了过分的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.92,0:20:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.86,0:21:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是有没有人知道\N西里露森林在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.19,0:21:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里应该是有复活圣水的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.63,0:21:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！蝴蝶蛹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.40,0:21:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.70,0:21:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这条村\N很快便会恢复蓝天白云了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.92,0:21:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是没可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.79,0:21:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算希度罗拿不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.22,0:21:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五界层的天空\N也被多恶达诅咒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.29,0:21:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜，难得蝴蝶出生了\N也没有给它休息的花朵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.33,0:21:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是为何没有花草树木的世界\N会有蝴蝶蛹的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.44,0:21:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在希度罗拿的河流处\N拾到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.24,0:21:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是说某一处\N有蝴蝶居住的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.81,0:21:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那便是西里露森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.68,0:21:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊，跟着那蝴蝶\N也许可以去到西里露森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.68,0:21:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.02,0:21:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走了，再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.89,0:21:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.75,0:22:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路小心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.22,0:22:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸，我一定…\N一定会救你的


